result.notes: This survey was undertaken by Cefas as part of the CEFAS Historic surveys; ... Survey took place between 17/06/1969 and 01/07/1969 on Corella Equipment used during this survey : - Lowestoft No 3 trawl with 60mm CodEnd tickler off - Lowestoft No 3 trawl with 60mm CodEnd tickler on - Lowestoft No 3 trawl with 60mm CodEnd with cover tickler off - Lowestoft No 3 trawl with 60mm CodEnd with cover tickler on Survey operations were undertaken on 44 stations 33 different species were caught on this survey
